            <li class="list-group-item lead pb-3" id='capabilities'>Capabilities
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#top">Back to top</a></li>
              
              <d1 class="row">
                <dt class="col-sm-4 ps-4 pt-2">User Capabilities</dt>
                  <dd class="col-sm-8 pt-2">
                    <p>Users can reserve aircraft for a specific hour and date, and specify whether an instructor is needed.<br>
                    Users can edit the personal information in their profile.<br>
                    Users can add "flights" to a reservation on or after the day of the flight and checkout via Stripe, cash, or check.<br>
                    Users cannot edit another member's flights or reservations.</p>
                  </dd>
                <dt class="col-sm-4 ps-4 pt-2">Instructor Capabilities</dt>
                  <dd class="col-sm-8 pt-2">
                    <p>Instructors can edit or delete another member's flights or reservations.<br>
                    Instructors can view their total flight time as an instructor and view the flight totals of other instructors.<br>
                    Instructors can send a 'Field Status Update' to the ESC google group.</p>
                  </dd>
                <dt class="col-sm-4 ps-4 pt-2">User Admin Capabilities</dt>
                  <dd class="col-sm-8 pt-2">
                    <p>User Admins can edit or delete another member's flights or reservations
                    User Admins can edit another member's profile information.<br>
                    User Admins can assign and edit memberships for users.<br>
                    User Admins can assign and edit the aircraft that members are allowed to reserve.</p>
                  </dd>
                  <dt class="col-sm-4 ps-4 pt-2">Club Admin Capabilities</dt>
                  <dd class="col-sm-8 pt-2">
                    <p>Club Admins can edit and add days and hours of operation.<br>
                    Club Admins can send a 'Field Status Update' to the ESC google group.<br>
                    Club Admins can download full flight logs to reconcile with payment portal and edit payment status for reconciliation</p>
                  </dd>
                  <dt class="col-sm-4 ps-4 pt-2">Site Admin Capabilities</dt>
                  <dd class="col-sm-8 pt-2">
                    <p>Site Admins can edit and add aircraft managed within the club.<br>
                    Site Admins can edit the tow fee pricing schedule.<br>
                    Site Admins can edit or add different membership types and pricing</p>
                  </dd>
                </d1> 
